HEADWORD: Double first
<hw>Dou"ble first`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Eng. Universities)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A degree of the first class both in classics and
mathematics.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>One who gains at examinations the
highest honor both in the classics and the mathematics.</def>
